attributes.documentation:
TokenPool is TokenContainer with 4 level pool structure: 
 Super Pool (Level 0), Pool (Level 1), Sub Pool (Level 2) and Token (Level 3)
 Level       Container / Member
 ------------------------------------------------
   0         SuperPool
   1              |______Pool
   2                      |______SubPool
   3                                |_______Token
